imdb.plot outline: Sabina Astudillo comes from a humble and poor background and dreams of day being rich and famous. Tired of being poor, she decides to leave her small town and head to the capital city in search of a better life. This is where she meets Leonardo Santander, presidential candidate and the favorite among the voters. Sabina is ambitious and sets her eyes on him and starts to orchestrate a plan to get close to him and later seduce him. Sabina gets help from Aníbal owner of the theater where she works and Domingo, a stylist who will teach her etiquette and once everything is in place, the plan starts rolling. However, Sabina wasn't expecting to fall in love with Mariano, a young theater director. This is when Sabina feels true love but realizes that in order to get where she wants, love has to be put aside and sacrifices need to be made and breaks up with Mariano. Sabina enters the life of Leonardo and his family, once she wins their trust; one by one they start to fall. Thanks to lies and manipulation, Sabina becomes the First Lady, but behind this accomplishment comes envy, intrigue, and true love are threatening to take away what she accomplished.
imdb.title: Primera Dama
plot: Sabina Astudillo is a ordinary, young but ambitious woman who is willing to do anything to seduce Leonardo Sandander a presidential candidate to become the First lady of Chile.::Anonymous

synopsis: Sabina Astudillo is a humble young woman with strong desires to emerge economically and socially, fast and without work. So she left the country life and move to the city.At first come to live in the house of his cousin Federico, a young theatrical producer married to Paula, who has been living in the capital. Through Federico, Sabina meets Mariano, a talented theater director who awaken the passion in it.The second ally of the young girl will be Aníbal Rodríguez, an unscrupulous and ambitious man, theater owner, who sees in the young a chance to win a place in the Chilean political arena.To reach the city and get along at first, Sabina managed to steals two million pesos to his eternal love: Caetano. Fooled by her sweet smile and words of love, the naive young man spent his life savings to someone he thought would finally be his future wife. Upon learning of the deception which starred his daughter, Star, the working mother of Sabina, decides to go after her, hoping to reach the city to recover his honor and his family, and straighten out once and for all his troubled daughter, who has caused her and her family the shame of the neighborhood.Star come to the capital without knowing anyone. With one hand in front and one behind and have to put aside their pride to stay and live the early days at the home of "Diablo" José, the father of her children who left twenty years ago to seek their fortune from Santiago and never returned. The "Devil" Joseph became a legend in his old neighborhood of the village, and in honor of him, Sabina was called "Devil's Daughter", when they began to realize that he had inherited his father's ambitious personality .Over time, Star will take his other two children to live with her: Angel, an insatiable bohemian man and a great protector of his mother, he will go nuts with the beautiful cosmopolitan women and fall in love with Luciana, the musical actress, and the youngest daughter, Emma, a young romantic who find love where she least expect it and with who should not.There will be many steps for Sabina to climb to the top. First gain the trust of Bruna, Leonardo's wife and mother of Diego and Cristina. The tired and frustrated sad lady lives a marriage where love and intimacy have been left in second place to prioritize the political career of her husband. So she lives recalling his younger years where she had the desire to do great things in life. Tired of her monotonous life, without apparent end and living through the stories of their children, she decided to return to school and finish his career in architecture, which left truncated to marry Leonardo. Needing an assistant to order her student's agenda and future first lady issues, the woman hired Sabina without knowing she will go live at her home and it will destroy her life.Leonardo, who disagrees his wife return to the university, since beginning his candidacy stage needs her closely than ever, Sabina will ally in its goal of returning home Bruna. The relationship between her husband and his assistant will awaken the jealousy of the woman, who will be realizing that Sabina is not what everyone think.
